WEBVTT

00:00.079 --> 00:03.899
Meet the smallest monkey in the world, the pygmy marmoset.

00:04.801 --> 00:06.996
An adult will fit in the palm of your hand.

00:07.548 --> 00:13.304
Being so tiny makes it hard to know who's friend, foe, or food.

00:16.645 --> 00:20.985
There's a whole wide world, living beneath our feet.

00:21.789 --> 00:22.873
Don't believe me?

00:23.496 --> 00:24.642
Look closer.

00:28.479 --> 00:38.155
In a land of giants, it's the smallest creatures that make the biggest difference.

00:41.219 --> 00:43.906
A midwife toad on a dangerous mission.

00:44.492 --> 00:49.965
His precious eggs need to get to water fast and he'll risk his life to do it.

